1.  Our greatest nukes are not just on the high end mobs, they are on the frigging item table, not the spell table.  This is unique among all other spell drops.  This was changed for one of those spells, and it rarely appears on lesser mobs now, but either spell makes such gems as Emmisary of Thule and that high shaman Slow look nearly vendor bought.  <br>
